g technique is, the less efficient it\nwill be.\n  Conclusion. For effectiveness, we observe that the existing automated testing\ntechniques are not effective enough, and currently they achieve nearly half of\nthe desired level of effectiveness. For efficiency, we observe that current\nautomated testing techniques are not efficient enough.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 Dec 2018 04:50:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-01"}
